            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>

    <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PS5</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a></li><li><a href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a></li>    </ul>

    
    <p><span>Physical edition pre-orders now available.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><em><a title="Games > Bubsy in: The Purrfect Collection [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/bubsy-in-the-purrfect-collection">Bubsy in: The Purrfect Collection</a></em> will launch digitally for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,117 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [7,691 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [23,918 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3039890/Bubsy_in_The_Purrfect_Collection/" target="_blank">Steam</a> on September 9, publishers <a title="Companies > Atari [199 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/atari">Atari</a> and <a title="Companies > Limited Run Games [208 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/limited-run-games">Limited Run Games</a> announced. Physical edition pre-orders are available now via <a href="https://atari.com/collections/bubsy-in-the-purrfect-collection" target="_blank">Atari Store</a>. <span id="more-984603"></span></p><p>Here is an overview of the collection, via Atari:</p><blockquote><p>Is Bubsy a celebrated icon from the mascot wars of the early ’90s or a platforming punchline? <em>Bubsy in: The Purrfect Collection</em> explores the franchise’s troubled history and enduring popularity. A playable history that includes games, artifacts, and interviews. What could possibly go wrong?</p><p>Included titles:</p><ul><li><em>Bubsy in Fractured Furry Tales</em> (Jaguar)</li><li><em>Bubsy in Claws Encounters of the Furred Kind</em> (Genesis, <a title="Platforms > SNES" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/snes">Super Nintendo Entertainment System</a>, Super Famicon)</li><li><em>Bubsy II</em> (<a title="Platforms > Game Boy [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/game-boy">Game Boy</a>, Genesis, Super Nintendo Entertainment System)</li><li><em>Bubsy 3D</em> (<a title="Platforms > PlayStation [48,242 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation">PlayStation</a>)</li></ul></blockquote><!-- AD: content -->
        <p>Watch a new trailer below.</p><h2><span>Release Date Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="Bubsy in: The Purrfect Collection Release Date Trailer" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/APBdZWwUeBE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2025/08/bubsy-in-the-purrfect-collection-launches-september-9]]></content:encoded>
